Ques 03 — College Course Allocation System.

Project Overview
----------------
Develop a Spring Core application to assign courses to faculty using constructor injection configured in XML.

Classes
-------
Course: courseId, courseName
Faculty: facultyId, name, course (dependency)

System Description
------------------
Course details are injected into faculty objects at creation time.

Real-Time Scenario
------------------
Used in college management systems to allocate courses to faculty members.

Expected Output
---------------
Display faculty and course details
